file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'http://ad.networknt.com/v1'
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: API AD for aggregate microservices pattern
  description: API AD is called by API AA along with another two APIs
  contact:
    email: stevehu@gmail.com
  license:
    name: Apache 2.0
    url: 'http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html'
paths:
  /data:
    get:
      description: Return an array of strings collected from down stream APIs
      operationId: listData
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                title: ArrayOfStrings
                type: array
                items:
                  type: string
              examples:
                response:
                  value:
                    - Message 1
                    - Message 2
      security:
        - ad_auth:
            - ad.w
            - ad.r
components:
  securitySchemes:
    ad_auth:
      type: oauth2
      flows:
        clientCredentials:
          authorizationUrl: 'http://localhost:8080/oauth2/code'
          scopes:
            ad.w: write access
            ad.r: read access
